{
  "stem": "12904.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we eventually left, but not before we had terrible argument with these two great big Bavarians who wanted to fight my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had done nothing, and he had just had open heart surgery and you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So anyway my sister said, I'll never go back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I went in '78.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had a humanist conference in London, and I was in Spain with a friend, visited Spain before the conference.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then told my relatives-- because the first time I went back in '67 and in '69 I was with my friend-- they did not ask me to stay in their house and they had a big house.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was my cousins.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I found out later, because I think that nobody would know that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they put me up in a little hotel nearby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wrote, at that time, in '78, that I would visit them only if they let me stay in their house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If not I would not visit Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would visit my cousin in Ulm-- it was not far from Stuttgart, the one cousin who had been married to a cousin of my father's.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had been married and was very faithful to him, also a Christian woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would just visit her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my aunt wrote, sure you can stay with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was when all this-- when that I shouldn't tell anybody who I was, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the articles on the Holocaust and on the rescuers have been published both by the and the I had published some articles before then on mental health issues, professional issues, and in occupational therapy.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I established a children's unit at Elgin State Hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
